
COMMAND:
   monk <text> or monkey <text> 

EXAMPLES:

   monk  hi all                        [*Monk*] hi all
   monkey gives all a banana           Fritz gives all a banana

ART:
  Guildtalk is the ability of a strong mental group to 
  communicate with each other. This strong conzentration
  effort sends your message to all your guildmembers.
  If you use legends as text in the monk command as:
  'monk legends' you get a list of logedon legends of  
  our guild.

COST:
    none

